        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Well, here, I wasn’t gonna read this one, but I will. I’ll start anyway so everything is under control. It’s called \"Cuba\". It’s a rather strange story in that the individual involved was someone I met and felt somewhat sorry for if I may be permitted to feel sorry about anybody."
